    "en": {
      "title": "The woman who pushed the Pradeshiya Sabha member into the river",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A woman who attacked a member of the Pradeshiya Sabha and pushed him into the river has been arrested.",
        "The woman also robbed money and property from the said woman Pradeshiya Sabha member.",
        "The woman has been charged with assaulting and injuring a member of the Ambalangoda Pradeshiya Sabha in Kollupitiya area on May 9 and pushing him into the Pere Vavi.",
        "Police said the suspect was arrested based on a complaint received at the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit.",
        "A 26-year-old woman from Kollupitiya area has been arrested. (a)"
      ],
